cs.LG, cs.DC, cs.DS, cs.CV, cs.NE 

This paper is primarily focused on the optimization of deep neural networks using asynchronous stochastic gradient descent in a distributed computing environment. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of cloud computing, which could fall under cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) or cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). The datasets used in the evaluation are image datasets, which could fall under cs.CV (Computer Vision). Finally, the paper discusses convergence rates, which could fall under cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms).
